Digital Gauge
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph  FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
Digital gauges are perfect for displaying output values that use alpha-numeric characters in a virtual digital display. The following are samples that illustrate the entire functionality of a digital gauge. 
</Paragraph> 
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Digital Gauge Demo</Bold> - This sample demonstrates the more powerful functionalities such as 7-segment display, 14-segment display, and segment space and width. In addition, this gauge has options for customizing its appearance.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"> <Bold>Digital Frame Demo</Bold> - This sample demonstrates the different frame types of the digital gauge and also its functionalities, such as segment display, segment space and width, as well as character space, height, and count.</Paragraph>

